; Coverage test for account.cc get_note (L291-293), get_subcount via 'n'
; (L468-469), get_count via 'N' (L497-498), and get_total via 'O'
; (L502-503). Exercises corresponding lookup switch branches.

account Expenses:Food
    note This is a food account

2024/01/01 Grocery
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash

test bal --format "%(n)|%(N)|%(O)|%(note)|%(account)\n"
1|1|$-10.00||Assets:Cash
1|1|$10.00|This is a food account|Expenses:Food
0|2|0||
end test
